    {
      "id": "SeKAmXZlIGRvbmUgJDJN",
      "text": "I’ve done $2M in income in 2.5 years as a solopreneur.\n\nAnd I didn't write a single line of code.\n\nMy 14 \"must use\" no-code tools:\n\n[ thread]",
      "author": "thejustinwelsh",
