    {
      "id": "aVBob25lIDVzIHdhcyB0",
      "text": "iPhone 5s was the best design ergonomically. Perfect size to reach across the screen with one thumb, no camera bulge, fingerprint sensor, nice materials, and 33% lighter than the latest iPhone 17 Air.",
