    {
      "id": "VGhlIG51YW5jZSBoZXJl",
      "text": "The nuance here is important: people want to post their experiences, not re-live them.\n\nProjection, not reflection. \n\nSurface, not depth. \n\nIt’s a strange trend that we have collectively agreed to enjoy things a little less so that our peers can see us perform enjoyment.",
