    {
      "id": "UGlubmVkClN0ZWZhbiBH",
      "text": "Pinned\nStefan Georgi\n@StefanGeorgi\n·\nFeb 10\n Article\nI Did Dozens of 1:1 Calls With $3MM-$300MM Brand Owners. Here's Where They All Get Stuck. \nLast month I added 1:1 calls for the members of my CA Pro Mastermind. These are all online business owners doing between $3MM/year and $300MM/year in revenue…\nAnd while they also can submit unlimited...\n8\n8\n133\n23K",
      "author": "StefanGeorgi",
      "platform": "x",
