    {
      "id": "VG9kYXkgSSBzYXkgZ29v",
      "text": "Today I say goodbye to my 30s. It was a wild decade:\n\n-Launched my first supplement company (Holy Land Health) in 2015 and went from $1MM rev that year to $23MM the second year.\n\n-Had to meet with 9 district attorneys in Oakland after they sent me a letter about that company (it",
      "author": "StefanGeorgi",
      "platform": "x",
      "verticals": [
        "direct_response",
        "copywriting"
      ],
      "engagement": {
        "likes": 0,
        "replies": 0
      },
      "minedAt": "2026-05-27T08:52:04.704Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "SSdtIGFib3V0IHRvIHR1",
      "text": "I'm about to turn 40 and one weird thing I keep thinking about is how the \"voice\" inside my head is basically the same as it was in my 20s, or even my teens. \n\nI don't mean I haven't matured or evolved. I'm infinitely more confident and calm today than I was back then...\n\nBut it",
      "author": "StefanGeorgi",
      "platform": "x",
      "verticals": [
        "direct_response",
        "copywriting"
      ],
      "engagement": {
        "likes": 0,
        "replies": 0
      },
      "minedAt": "2026-05-27T08:52:04.704Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UHJlc2lkZW50IFRydW1w",
      "text": "President Trump is so damn impressive and here’s why (don’t read if you have TDS)...\n\nFirst off, he continues to run the SAME playbook on repeat, and the whole world keeps falling for it. This playbook is:\n\n1. Take an extreme position.\n2. Take initial actions that show he’s",
      "author": "StefanGeorgi",
      "platform": "x",
      "verticals": [
        "direct_response",
        "copywriting"
      ],
      "engagement": {
        "likes": 0,
        "replies": 0
      },
      "minedAt": "2026-05-27T08:52:04.704Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "QSBmZXcgd2Vla3MgSSAg",
      "text": "A few weeks I  attended Grant Cardone’s private mastermind at his HQ in Miami.\n\nGrant shared several lessons he used to build $150m dollar companies and amass a networth of over one billion dollars.\n\nHere’s 44 things he told me.",
      "author": "StefanGeorgi",
      "platform": "x",
      "verticals": [
        "direct_response",
        "copywriting"
      ],
      "engagement": {
        "likes": 0,
