      "id": "4oCcQ2hhLWNoaW5n4oCd",
      "text": "“Cha-ching”\n\n$5,000 hit my PayPal account.\n\n“This has to be a typo...” I thought to myself.\n\nSo I messaged him.\n\n“Hey, did you mean to send $5,000?”\n\nHis response:\n\n“Yeah, is that enough?”\n\nAnd just like that, Ghostwriting completely changed my life trajectory.\n\nHere’s the story",
